# Link to this sectionTFLite、ONNX、CoreML、TensorRT 导出#

📚 本指南介绍了如何将训练好的 YOLOv5 🚀 模型从 [PyTorch](https://www.ultralytics.com/glossary/pytorch) 导出为多种部署格式，包括 ONNX、TensorRT、CoreML 等。

## Link to this section开始之前#

Clone repo and install [requirements.txt](https://github.com/ultralytics/yolov5/blob/master/requirements.txt) in a [**Python >=3.8.0**](https://www.python.org/) environment, including [**PyTorch >=1.8**](https://pytorch.org/get-started/locally/). [Models](https://github.com/ultralytics/yolov5/tree/master/models) and [datasets](https://github.com/ultralytics/yolov5/tree/master/data) download automatically from the latest YOLOv5 [release](https://github.com/ultralytics/yolov5/releases).
    
    
    git clone https://github.com/ultralytics/yolov5 # clone
    cd yolov5
    pip install -r requirements.txt # install

有关 [TensorRT](https://developer.nvidia.com/tensorrt) 导出示例（需要 GPU），请参阅我们的 Colab [笔记本](https://colab.research.google.com/github/ultralytics/yolov5/blob/master/tutorial.ipynb#scrollTo=VTRwsvA9u7ln&line=2&uniqifier=1) 附录部分。[![Open In Colab](https://colab.research.google.com/assets/colab-badge.svg)](https://colab.research.google.com/github/ultralytics/yolov5/blob/master/tutorial.ipynb)

## Link to this section支持的导出格式#

YOLOv5 推理官方支持 12 种格式：

性能提示

  * 导出为 ONNX 或 OpenVINO 可获得高达 3 倍的 CPU 加速。请参阅 [CPU 基准测试](https://github.com/ultralytics/yolov5/pull/6613)。
  * 导出为 TensorRT 可获得高达 5 倍的 GPU 加速。请参阅 [GPU 基准测试](https://github.com/ultralytics/yolov5/pull/6963)。



格式| `export.py --include`| 模型  
---|---|---  
[PyTorch](https://pytorch.org/)| -| `yolov5s.pt`  
[TorchScript](/zh/integrations/torchscript)| `torchscript`| `yolov5s.torchscript`  
[ONNX](/zh/integrations/onnx)| `onnx`| `yolov5s.onnx`  
[OpenVINO](/zh/integrations/openvino)| `openvino`| `yolov5s_openvino_model/`  
[TensorRT](/zh/integrations/tensorrt)| `engine`| `yolov5s.engine`  
[CoreML](/zh/integrations/coreml)| `coreml`| `yolov5s.mlmodel`  
[TensorFlow SavedModel](/zh/integrations/tf-savedmodel)| `saved_model`| `yolov5s_saved_model/`  
[TensorFlow GraphDef](/zh/integrations/tf-graphdef)| `pb`| `yolov5s.pb`  
[TensorFlow Lite](/zh/integrations/tflite)| `tflite`| `yolov5s.tflite`  
[TensorFlow Edge TPU](/zh/integrations/edge-tpu)| `edgetpu`| `yolov5s_edgetpu.tflite`  
[TensorFlow.js](/zh/integrations/tfjs)| `tfjs`| `yolov5s_web_model/`  
[PaddlePaddle](/zh/integrations/paddlepaddle)| `paddle`| `yolov5s_paddle_model/`  
  
